overview: The user initiated a comprehensive aesthetic review for their sleep
  questionnaire app, aiming to transform its generic appearance into a more
  polished and calming experience. The process began with an in-depth analysis
  of existing styles, leading to the implementation of a new sleep-themed color
  palette, subtle background gradients, and redesigned core UI components like
  checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders, and progress bars. All questionnaire
  sections, including the intro and report, were updated for visual consistency,
  replacing old gray boxes with refined card-style groupings and themed alerts.
  A critical console error related to null input values was also addressed by
  implementing a robust fix in the Input component. The iterative process
  involved multiple rounds of refinement based on code review and user feedback,
  culminating in a cohesive and professional aesthetic that aligns with the
  app's purpose.
